mpting to RP the game. At this point, I'm never going to reroll again - I've been a ranger for my very first guy for 5 min, 3 different SK's, and now a BST - and this is it. While I wanted to play a pure caster at some point, I prefer my friends and community here - so next time I get bored? /rude you SOE - I'll find a new world to explore. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=decius1@firionavie>Decius1</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#A62A2A>(1/5/04 1:06 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4779.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   re</span><hr size=1> The one character per account rule used to help with identifying bad people. But in the days of 65 in 24 hours, multiple accounts, stormhammer transfers, ebaying and general pandemonium anyone who wants to hide their identity can do it pretty easily.<br>
